# Common Interview Questions

## Question 01
Why do you want to leave your current position?
## Response 01
I've reached my full potential in the role and I'm now seeking a role where I'll be pushed and challenged. 

## Question 02
Where do you see yourself in N years? 
## Response 02
I see myself in a senior role in your company.

## Question 03
Do you have any questions?
## Response 03
If you hire me today, how will you know in a year's time that I was the right fit?
